				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Have you considered opening up nominations for chat reviewers as well?</p> </blockquote> <p>Chat's more difficult to check up on since that would potentially necessitate poring through logs, but I'm happy to receive nominations for chat reviewers provided that enough people vouch for them! I personally use chat nigh-exclusively for seeking reviewers, so I definitely know how much time and brainpower is devoted to keeping those avenues of review running.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
