					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9804105#post-4104974</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9804105/reviewers-spotlight-archive#post-4104974</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 01 Jan 2019 06:10:10 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>As part of an effort to give our forum reviewers their well-deserved time in the sun, the event features block has been replaced with a 4-times-a-month Reviewers' Spotlight!</p> <p>If you're looking to become a site reviewer, here are two good places to start:</p> <ul> <li><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-9804362/so-you-want-to-be-a-concept-reviewer">http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-9804362/so-you-want-to-be-a-concept-reviewer</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-9804215/so-you-want-to-be-a-draft-reviewer">http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-9804215/so-you-want-to-be-a-draft-reviewer</a></li> </ul> <p>To nominate reviewers who have helped you or other authors, please send me (Zyn) their names via wikidot PM.</p> <p>Happy 2019, everyone!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
